00:18:53.621 --> 00:18:54.260
Go have a meal.

00:18:54.461 --> 00:18:55.540
Come, I'll lead the way.

00:18:56.300 --> 00:18:57.340
Please, Grandmother.

00:19:00.701 --> 00:19:01.181
Lord Xue.

00:19:01.580 --> 00:19:02.701
With considerable effort,

00:19:03.181 --> 00:19:04.941
I learned
from Xue family's elderly servants

00:19:05.300 --> 00:19:06.100
that 13 years ago,

00:19:06.312 --> 00:19:08.680
the Xue family sent
Xue Fugui's illegitimate son Xue Youshou

00:19:08.680 --> 00:19:09.340
away

00:19:09.701 --> 00:19:10.500
to the south.

00:19:12.580 --> 00:19:13.701
What else?

00:19:14.221 --> 00:19:14.941
Tell me in detail.

00:19:15.901 --> 00:19:17.500
According to them,

00:19:18.221 --> 00:19:19.300
the Xue family

00:19:19.421 --> 00:19:21.060
has forbidden them from discussing this.

00:19:21.580 --> 00:19:23.540
Xue Youshou has never returned.

00:19:24.461 --> 00:19:26.500
The Xue family sent him so far away

00:19:26.901 --> 00:19:29.300
with annual payments
worth two decades of commoners' income.

00:19:30.381 --> 00:19:32.981
He must be the former Crown Prince.

00:19:33.861 --> 00:19:34.300
Go get him

00:19:34.981 --> 00:19:35.780
in the south.

00:19:36.008 --> 00:19:36.580
Understood.

00:19:42.181 --> 00:19:43.060
Xue Hexu.

00:19:44.661 --> 00:19:46.141
You said to be my family.

00:19:46.981 --> 00:19:47.981
How ridiculous!

00:20:03.820 --> 00:20:05.221
You claimed to be my family,

00:20:06.260 --> 00:20:07.181
demanding my trust.

00:20:08.300 --> 00:20:10.260
Yet you hid
the former Crown Prince's whereabouts

00:20:10.780 --> 00:20:11.661
from me.

00:20:12.820 --> 00:20:13.701
I truly don't know.

00:20:16.300 --> 00:20:18.621
Our entire family has never met him.

00:20:20.020 --> 00:20:20.941
Perhaps our Xue family

00:20:22.621 --> 00:20:23.941
has no connection to that prince.

00:20:25.981 --> 00:20:26.621
You

00:20:28.260 --> 00:20:29.540
expect me to trust you?

00:20:31.540 --> 00:20:32.861
(I chose to trust you,)

00:20:33.421 --> 00:20:34.941
(yet you lie to me all along.)

00:20:40.181 --> 00:20:40.981
Sincerity...

00:20:49.100 --> 00:20:49.780
You liar!

00:20:59.221 --> 00:21:00.421
(From today on,)

00:21:01.540 --> 00:21:02.981
(I won't trust you anymore.)

00:21:09.421 --> 00:21:09.941
Your Majesty.

00:21:10.621 --> 00:21:12.100
I found out the former Crown Prince

00:21:12.260 --> 00:21:13.540
likely hides in distant regions.

00:21:13.780 --> 00:21:15.820
I'm here to request your permission

00:21:16.020 --> 00:21:16.820
to go find him.

00:21:18.141 --> 00:21:21.300
If you fail to bring me his head

00:21:21.340 --> 00:21:22.500
this time,

00:21:23.020 --> 00:21:24.340
I shall punish you.

00:21:25.100 --> 00:21:26.141
Yes.

00:21:26.280 --> 00:21:27.784
(Funds Pre-approved)

00:21:31.060 --> 00:21:33.260
This is the funds for this mission,

00:21:33.780 --> 00:21:36.461
enough for you
to get personnel and resources.

00:21:42.461 --> 00:21:44.100
The sum is exceptionally large.

00:21:44.461 --> 00:21:45.981
I may not require this much.

00:21:46.381 --> 00:21:48.540
Just take it.

00:21:49.141 --> 00:21:50.260
You serve me,

00:21:50.621 --> 00:21:52.540
naturally, I will treat you well.

00:21:52.901 --> 00:21:54.901
Remember, efficiency comes first.

00:21:55.381 --> 00:21:57.740
Don't bother other things.

00:21:58.580 --> 00:21:59.381
If you meet trouble,

00:21:59.701 --> 00:22:01.820
I'll resolve them.

00:22:02.820 --> 00:22:04.141
After eliminating the rebel,

00:22:05.141 --> 00:22:06.861
massacre people

00:22:07.820 --> 00:22:10.260
of Lord Dingyuan's Mansion.

00:22:13.221 --> 00:22:13.740
Your Majesty.

