of your husband.

00:22:28.181 --> 00:22:28.981
I meant no offense.

00:22:29.381 --> 00:22:31.020
Harboring the former dynasty's rebel

00:22:31.381 --> 00:22:33.540
deserves severe punishment.

00:22:33.941 --> 00:22:35.300
Yet the Lord Dingyuan's Mansion

00:22:35.580 --> 00:22:37.020
